original_title: Power Rangers Mystic Force: Legendary Catastros
overview: The Rangers learn the story of Koragg's magical horse - Catastros and how he was thought to be untamable. In a battle with Koragg, Nick gets lost in another dimension. Can he find a way to heal an injured Catastros and can his friends find a way to save him?
title: Power Rangers Mystic Force: Legendary Catastros
